Author: phm87#7395
Content:
ok it is working now, I had to do this:
```git clone https://github.com/KomodoPlatform/atomicDEX-API/
cd atomicDEX-API
rustup install nightly
rustup override set nightly

cargo clean 
cargo build --features native -vv``` I needed to add ``rustup install nightly
 rustup override set nightly`` and now the build seems to build
